		<h2>Summary</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Requested in <span class="info">5</span>/<span class="info">26</span> calls</li>
			<li>Requested in <span class="info">5</span>/<span class="info">19</span> pure calls (<a href="../sle2022/index.html#cfp">2022</a>–<a href="../sle2026/index.html#cfp">2026</a> with the longest streak of <span class="info">5</span> years)</li>

			<li>Primary tagged in <span class="info">1</span>/<span class="info">26</span> paper bundles</li>
			<li>Primary tagged in <span class="info">1</span>/<span class="info">19</span> pure proceedings (<a href="../sle2024/index.html#lop">2024</a>–<a href="../sle2024/index.html#lop">2024</a> with the longest streak of <span class="info">1</span> years)</li>

			<li>Secondary tagged in <span class="info">2</span>/<span class="info">26</span> paper bundles</li>
